div.p: Award of the best poster (Ms M. Bakour (1st on the right), Ph.D student, Laboratory of Physiology-Pharmacology-Environmental Health, Faculty of Sciences Dhar El Mehraz, University Sidi Mohamed Ben Abdallah, Fez, Morocco) during the gala evening. The award has been delivered by the members of the organizing committee: Prof Dr. A. El Midaoui, Pr. Y. Filali-Zegzouti and Pr. L. El Rhaffari.
